      "lastInstructions": "want to send a reminder out for our boots and bourbon event this saturday may 2nd, 2026 doors open at 5:30 PM -- No reservation needed.. heres some details on the event.\n\n🤠✨ BOOTS & BOURBON: NEON NIGHTS at The Quarry ✨🤠\nWe’re turning up the lights and bringing the energy on Saturday, May 2nd 🔥\nGet ready for a night of line dancing, bourbon, and neon vibes under the lights 💃🥃\n🚪 Doors Open: 5:30 PM\n🎶 Line Dance Instruction: 6:00 PM (Evan VanScoyk)\n💃 Social Dancing: 7:00 PM\nWhether you’re a pro on the dance floor or just getting started, this is your night to grab your boots and join the party 🤠\n21+ | $5 Cover\n📍 The Quarry\n3960 Highway Z\nWentzville, MO\nTag your crew, throw on your neon + western gear, and let’s pack the dance floor 🔥\n👉 This one’s going to be a BIG night… don’t miss it. See less\n\ni want to promote our 70 - 80 = 90s bingo\n\nOur Music Bingo nights have been SELLING OUT… so we’re turning it up.\nhttps://thequarrystl.com/quarry-event-detail...\n🎶 70s • 80s • 90s MUSIC BINGO\n📅 May 22nd, 2026\n📍 The Quarry\nIf you missed our 80s & 90s nights… this is your shot 👇\nWe’re bringing ALL 3 DECADES together for one insane night of throwbacks 🎧\n🎧 Live DJ Earl Draper\n🎟️ $20 tickets\n👥 Tables of 4\n🍻 Beer bucket OR bottle of wine per table\n🏆 Prizes all night long\n⏰ Doors open at 5:30 PM\n🎶 Bingo starts at 7 PM\nhttps://thequarrystl.com/quarry-event-detail...\nGrab your crew, pick your decade, and let’s run it back at The Quarry!\n\nI want to promote our new menu items with our pizzas and pretzels now available at the quarry.",
