      "subject": "The dish we keep putting back on the menu",
      "htmlBody": "<div style=\"background:#f4f5f7;padding:2rem 1rem;font-family:'Montserrat',-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;color:#1c1f26;line-height:1.6;\">\n<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;padding:2rem 1.5rem;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);\">\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1rem;border-bottom:2px solid #9a7b2a;\">\n  <div style=\"font-family:'Playfair Display',Georgia,serif;font-size:1.8rem;color:#1c1f26;letter-spacing:0.02em;\">THE QUARRY</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;font-family:Georgia,serif;color:#2c2c2c;background:#ffffff;padding:32px 24px;\"><p style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;margin:0 0 20px;\">Some dishes earn a permanent place — this is one of them.</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 16px;\">Our pan-seared duck breast comes to the table with a crisp, rendered skin giving way to meat that's rosy and tender at the center. It sits over a celery root purée that's silky without being heavy, finished with a tart cherry reduction and a scattering of toasted hazelnuts for bite. It's the kind of plate that makes the table go quiet for a moment.</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 32px;\">Available now through the end of May, while the season holds. We'd recommend pairing it with a glass of our current Willamette Valley Pinot Noir — the kitchen had exactly that in mind when they built the dish.</p><a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/reservations\" style=\"display:inline-block;background-color:#9a7b2a;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.05em;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:3px;\">Reserve Your Table</a><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#6b6b6b;margin:40px 0 0;line-height:1.6;\">We'll see you at the table,<br><strong>The Quarry</strong></p></div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:2rem auto 0;padding:1.5rem 1rem;border-top:1px solid #e0e3e8;font-family:'Montserrat',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:0.75rem;color:#858d9e;text-align:center;line-height:1.5;\">\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\n    <strong style=\"color:#4b5263;\">The Quarry</strong> &middot; 3960 Highway Z, New Melle, MO 63385\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\n    <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;\">thequarrystl.com</a> &middot;\n    <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thequarrystl\" style=\"color:#9a7b2a;text-decoration:none;\">Facebook</a>\n  </div>\n  <div>\n    You're receiving this because you signed up, booked a reservation, or attended an event at The Quarry.\n    <a href=\"https://www.thequarrystl.com/unsubscribe?email={email}\" style=\"color:#858d9e;text-decoration:underline;\">Unsubscribe</a>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
      "innerHtml": "<div style=\"max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;font-family:Georgia,serif;color:#2c2c2c;background:#ffffff;padding:32px 24px;\"><p style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;margin:0 0 20px;\">Some dishes earn a permanent place — this is one of them.</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 16px;\">Our pan-seared duck breast comes to the table with a crisp, rendered skin giving way to meat that's rosy and tender at the center. It sits over a celery root purée that's silky without being heavy, finished with a tart cherry reduction and a scattering of toasted hazelnuts for bite. It's the kind of plate that makes the table go quiet for a moment.</p><p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 32px;\">Available now through the end of May, while the season holds. We'd recommend pairing it with a glass of our current Willamette Valley Pinot Noir — the kitchen had exactly that in mind when they built the dish.</p><a href=\"https://www.thequarrynewmelle.com/reservations\" style=\"display:inline-block;background-color:#9a7b2a;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.05em;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:3px;\">Reserve Your Table</a><p style=\"font-size:14px;color:#6b6b6b;margin:40px 0 0;line-height:1.6;\">We'll see you at the table,<br><strong>The Quarry</strong></p></div>",
